      • shouldMutate

        public boolean shouldMutate(G genotype)
        Determine if this mutator should be applied to the given genotype. This may be influenced by randomised processes so can not be relied upon to return the same value for the same genotype. This default implementation checks if the genotype is a clone of a single parent or a child of multiple parents and then compares either applyPercentageClones or applyPercentageRecombined accordingly to a randomly generated number to determine if this mutator should be applied.
